      },
    ]}
  />

  <!-- ── 10. FAQs ──────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <FaqAccordion
    tagline="FAQs"
    title="ERP-Integrated Field Service Management — questions answered"
    items={[
      {
        question: 'What is ERP-Integrated Field Service Management?',
        answer: 'ERP-Integrated FSM extends SAP to field technicians, allowing real-time work order updates, parts tracking, service reporting, and digital sign-offs — without modifying the ERP core.',
      },
      {
        question: 'Does UpBuff FSM replace SAP Service Management?',
        answer: 'No. UpBuff FSM complements SAP by enabling mobile-first execution for field technicians while keeping SAP as the authoritative system of record for all service data.',
      },
      {
        question: 'How does data synchronization work?',
        answer: 'UpBuff uses secure APIs — SAP OData, Service Layer, and BAPI — to synchronize data bi-directionally in real time between field devices and SAP.',
      },
      {
        question: 'Can technicians work offline?',
        answer: 'Yes. The platform supports fully offline operation. Technicians can complete jobs, capture photos, record parts usage, and collect signatures without connectivity. All data syncs securely when connection resumes.',
      },
      {
        question: 'Which SAP versions are supported?',
        answer: 'UpBuff FSM integrates with SAP S/4HANA (OData/RFC), SAP ECC (BAPI), and SAP Business One (Service Layer). Oracle and Epicor integrations are also supported via REST/SOAP APIs.',
      },
      {
        question: 'Is it secure for enterprise environments?',
        answer: 'Yes. Role-based access control, full audit logging, TLS encrypted communication, and controlled API-based integration ensure enterprise-grade security. ERP remains the system of record at all times.',
      },
    ]}
  />

  <SecuritySplit
    tagline="Get Started"
    title="Get started with ERP-Integrated CRM"
    subtitle="Whether you're a growing SAP Business One customer or a large enterprise on S/4HANA, UpBuff adapts to your ERP landscape."

    features={[
      {
        title: 'Schedule a Demo',
        description: 'See live ERP sync, mobile order capture, and pricing enforcement in action. Schedule a 30-minute demo with our SAP integration specialists.',
        href: '/contact',
      },
      {
        title: 'Join Partner Program',
        description: 'SAP reseller and ERP channel partner program for VARs and system integrators. Earn commissions on every UpBuff deployment you bring to market.',
        href: '/partners',
      },
      {
        title: 'Explore CRM Modules',
        description: 'Browse field sales, distribution management, collections, and performance reporting modules organized by industry and ERP platform.',
        href: '/solutions',
